Error: Error: "Connection Lost - Internal Exception: Java.Io.IOException: An Existing Connection Was Forcibly Closed By The Remote Host"

Cause: This Error Occurs When The Connection Between The Minecraft Client And Server Is Lost Due To A Server Crash, Network Interruption, Or Other Reasons.

Solution: 1. Restart your Minecraft client and try to reconnect to the server.

2. Check your internet connection and make sure it is stable.

3. If you are playing on a server that you do not control, ask the server
